      "widgets_values": [
        "A breathtakingly photorealistic portrait of a solitary woman, mid-twenties, with long, flowing auburn hair catching the dappled sunlight, wearing an elegant, crimson velvet gown that pools around her feet. She stands poised amidst a dense, ancient temperate forest, surrounded by towering moss-covered oak trees and ferns. The lighting is dramatic chiaroscuro, with shafts of golden, ethereal sunlight piercing through the thick canopy, casting deep, cool shadows across the forest floor. The mood is romantic and slightly melancholic. The color palette is dominated by deep emerald greens, rich mahogany browns, and vibrant scarlet red. Shot with a medium telephoto lens at eye level, utilizing a shallow depth of field to keep the focus intensely sharp on the woman while softly blurring the surrounding woods into painterly bokeh. Cinematic composition, hyperdetailed texture rendering on the velvet and bark."
